    <item>
      <title>近 9,800 起性犯罪案件在英国破碎的法院系统中陷入困境</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2023-12-18/does-the-uk-criminal-justice-system-still-work</link>
      <description><![CDATA[从人满为患的监狱到创纪录的法院积压案件，刑事司法系统正被推向崩溃边缘。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2023-12-18/does-the-uk-criminal-justice-system-still-work</guid>
