    <item>
      <title>日本首相的困境引发了对潜在继任者的猜测</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/who-s-waiting-in-the-wings-as-japan-s-premier-kishida-flounders</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本首相岸田文雄的任期可能屈指可数，最近的一项民意调查显示，绝大多数选民希望这位陷入困境的领导人最迟在 9 月份任期结束前辞去首相职务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/who-s-waiting-in-the-wings-as-japan-s-premier-kishida-flounders</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Dec 2023 03:30:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国计划对价值 290 亿美元的陆桥项目进行全球招标，以绕过马六甲海峡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/thailand-plans-global-bidding-for-29-billion-project-to-bypass-malacca-strait</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国计划对一个耗资 1 万亿泰铢（合 290 亿美元）的项目进行国际竞标，该项目旨在绕过马六甲海峡，大幅缩短印度洋和太平洋之间的航运时间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/thailand-plans-global-bidding-for-29-billion-project-to-bypass-malacca-strait</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Dec 2023 03:29:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
